16#ifndef RDATA_GENERIC_CDS_59_C
17#define RDATA_GENERIC_CDS_59_C
18
19#define RRTYPE_CDS_ATTRIBUTES 0
20
21#include <dns/ds.h>
22
23static inline isc_result_t
24fromtext_cds(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
25
26 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_cds);
27
28 return (generic_fromtext_ds(rdclass, type, lexer, origin, options,
29 target, callbacks));
30}
31
32static inline isc_result_t
33totext_cds(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
34
35 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_cds);
36
37 return (generic_totext_ds(rdata, tctx, target));
38}
39
40static inline isc_result_t
41fromwire_cds(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
42
43 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_cds);
44
45 return (generic_fromwire_ds(rdclass, type, source, dctx, options,
46 target));
47}
48
49static inline isc_result_t
50towire_cds(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
51 isc_region_t sr;
52
53 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_cds);
54 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
55
56 UNUSED(cctx);
57
58 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
59 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
60}
61
62static inline int
63compare_cds(ARGS_COMPARE) {
64 isc_region_t r1;
65 isc_region_t r2;
66
67 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
68 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
69 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_cds);
70 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
71 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
72
73 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
74 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
75 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
76}
77
78static inline isc_result_t
79fromstruct_cds(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
80
81 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_cds);
82
83 return (generic_fromstruct_ds(rdclass, type, source, target));
84}
85
86static inline isc_result_t
87tostruct_cds(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
88 dns_rdata_cds_t *cds = target;
89
90 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_cds);
91 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
92 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
93
94 /*
95 * Checked by generic_tostruct_ds().
96 */
97 cds->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
98 cds->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
99 ISC_LINK_INIT(&cds->common, link);
100
101 return (generic_tostruct_ds(rdata, target, mctx));
102}
103
104static inline void
105freestruct_cds(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
106 dns_rdata_cds_t *ds = source;
107
108 REQUIRE(ds != NULL);
109 REQUIRE(ds->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_cds);
110
111 if (ds->mctx == NULL)
112 return;
113
114 if (ds->digest != NULL)
115 isc_mem_free(ds->mctx, ds->digest);
116 ds->mctx = NULL;
117}
118
119static inline isc_result_t
120additionaldata_cds(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
121 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_cds);
122
123 UNUSED(rdata);
124 UNUSED(add);
125 UNUSED(arg);
126
127 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
128}
129
130static inline isc_result_t
131digest_cds(ARGS_DIGEST) {
132 isc_region_t r;
133
134 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_cds);
135
136 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
137
138 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
139}
140
141static inline bool
142checkowner_cds(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
143
144 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_cds);
145
146 UNUSED(name);
147 UNUSED(type);
148 UNUSED(rdclass);
149 UNUSED(wildcard);
150
151 return (true);
152}
153
154static inline bool
155checknames_cds(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
156
157 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_cds);
158
159 UNUSED(rdata);
160 UNUSED(owner);
161 UNUSED(bad);
162
163 return (true);
164}
165
166static inline int
167casecompare_cds(ARGS_COMPARE) {
168 return (compare_cds(rdata1, rdata2));
169}

171#endif /* RDATA_GENERIC_CDS_59_C */
